NOTE: Depends on the Image class found at ../Image-to-BMP/
and the math types found at ../Math

Contains assorted graphics utilities, most important of which is
a Wavefront OBJ file reader and MTL reader (note that they are 
anything but complete). And an PNG reader class.

Also included ins a header file that includes severa OpenGL header
files, working on both Linux and Mac OSX (the macros _LINUX or _OSX,
must be defined for either).